Functional:
ID F1    - The vehicles has to show the amount of people inside.
ID F2    - The vehicles has to show the induvidual people inside.
ID F3    - People have to be able to enter and leave the vehicles.
ID F4    - Information of avalible vehicles has to be send to the server whenever there is a change in the amount.
ID F5    - Vehicels have to be able to recive information / tasks from the server.
ID F6    - Vehicles have to confirm the received information.
ID F7    - Vehicles have to confirm the arrival at the place of operation to the server.
ID F8    - Vehicles have to send information about the people inside to the server when they leave the place of operation.

Non-Functional:
ID NF1   - 
